  // Post Your Latest News
  section.section-xl.bg-default.text-center
    .container
      h3 Post Your Latest News
      .row.row-50
        .col-md-6.col-xl-4
          // Post classic
          article.post-minimal

            +jpg('post-minimal-1-418x315')
            .post-classic-title
              h5: a(href=postLink) 10 Reasons to Buy Monstroid²

            .post-meta
              .group-xs
                a(href=postLink): time(datetime='2017') Jan.20, 2016
                span by Brian Williamson

            .post-classic-body
              p In this article, we would like to share with you why we think Monstroid² is a perfect template for your website and why you should buy it.
            .post-minimal-footer
              a(href=postLink).button.button-link read more

        .col-md-6.col-xl-4
          // Post classic
          article.post-minimal

            +jpg('post-minimal-5-418x315')
            .post-classic-title
              h5: a(href=postLink) How to Use Bootstrap Framework

            .post-meta
              .group-xs
                a(href=postLink): time(datetime='2017') Jan.20, 2016
                span by Brian Williamson

            .post-classic-body
              p Bootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS framework for developing responsive, mobile first projects on the web. Here’s how you can use it.
